**Example**: E-commerce site with 50,000 product pages, only 30,000 indexed.
- Crawl budget optimization → 45,000 pages indexed (15,000 more products discoverable)
- Average product page: 10 organic visits/month
- 15,000 new pages × 10 visits = 150,000 additional monthly visits
